FBIS4-6923 "dreas080__a94010" FBIS-EAS-94-080-A Daily Report 26 April 1994 ANNEX Japan Watanabe on Support for Hata Administration Watanabe on Support for Hata Administration OW2604064994 Tokyo Nikkei Telecom Database in Japanese 26 Apr 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY OW2604064994 Tokyo Nikkei Telecom Database Japanese BFN [From MAINICHI SHIMBUN 26 April Morning Edition] [Text] Michio Watanabe, Liberal Democratic Party member and former deputy prime minister and foreign minister, commented on the new administration led by Prime Minister Tsutomu Hata on 25 April. He said: "I would like (Hata) to carry out Shinseito's original policies. I will cooperate in implementing policies that are beneficial for Japan, and will not cooperate with those that are not."
